  "title": "7506 - Interior Designer | Eunos",
  "description": "<p>Working Days: Monday – Friday<br />Working Hours: 9am – 5.30pm<br />Salary: $ 3,000 – $ 4,800<br />Working Location: Eunos <br /><br />Industry: Interior Design & Construction Company<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and present creative design concepts based on client requirements and project objectives.</li><li>Prepare space planning layouts, mood boards, 3D visualizations and detailed construction drawings.</li><li>Source and select furniture, materials, lighting and finishes.</li><li>Manage project timelines, budgets and deliverables.</li><li>Coordinate and collaborate with architects, engineers and contractors to ensure design intent is executed accurately.</li><li>Conduct site visits to monitor construction progress and quality.</li><li>Stay updated on industry trends, new materials, and relevant regulations.<br /> </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or O-Level qualification in Interior Design or a related field, with several years of relevant working experience.</li><li>Proficient in AutoCAD, SketchUp, Revit or other design software.</li><li>Strong design portfolio demonstrating experience in residential, commercial or hospitality projects.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Chin See Min Reg No. : R22107450</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No. : 14C7279</strong></p>",
